<body>
    <h1>Assignment Based Deprovisioning (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC1=
9)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"AssignmentBasedDeprovisioning(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93=
UC19)-AssignmentBasedDeprovisioningworkflow">Assignment Based Deprovisionin=
g workflow</h3>
<p>Table-34</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4=
dab3a17-40c5-49dd-b90f-c44b5cec5584" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 330.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1469.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Assignment Based Deprovisioning</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>This Assignment Based Deprovisioning workflow covers removal in user wor=
k assignment</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Person Number&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>WORKRELATIONSHIP_PRIMARY_FLAG will be No</p></li>
<li>
<p>ASSIGNMENT_EFFECTIVE_START_DATE</p></li>
<li>
<p>ASSIGNMENT_EFFECTIVE_END_DATE</p></li>
<li>
<p>ASSIGNMENT_PRIMARY_FLAG</p></li>
<li>
<p>ASSIGNMENT_STATUS</p></li>
<li>
<p>TERMINATION_DATE</p></li>
<li>
<p>JOBCODE</p></li>
<li>
<p>ASSIGNMENT_ID=E2=80=8B</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>User should have a primary work relationship and ASSIGNMENT_PRIMARY_FLAG=
 is set to =E2=80=98No=E2=80=99.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>System Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should b=
e equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Employee</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Action Name</strong>=E2=80=99 should be equal to =E2=80=
=98<strong>End Assignment</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Assignment Status</strong>=E2=80=99 status is =E2=80=98=
<strong>Inactive-Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Users should have primary/secondary work Assignment assigned in SailPoin=
t IdentityIQ.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Secondary/Primary work assignment deprovisioning initiation for primary =
record in Oracle HCM Cloud.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ removes secondary work Assignment based on ASSIGNME=
NT_PRIMARY_FLAG .</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Secondary work Assignment deprovisioning process is triggered on removal=
 of secondary assignment in Oracle HCM Cloud feed</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
